abstract: Hanover, NJ, authorities report death of two construction workers after five-ton generator falls from crane at construction site.

headline.main: Five-Ton Generator Dropped From Crane Kills 2 in New Jersey

snippet: The mayor of Hanover Township, where the two men were killed on a construction site, said a strap on a crane lowering the generator snapped.
lead_paragraph: The mayor of Hanover Township, where the two men were killed on a construction site, said a strap on a crane lowering the generator snapped.
